item.title: THM - Walking An Application - Walkthrough
item.description: This series of walkthroughs aims to help out complete beginners with finishing the Web Fundamentals path on the TryHackMe (thm)1 website. It is based on the learning content provided in the Walking An Application room. Task 1 - Walking An Application Read the intro and the short breakdown about the room. Make sure to start the machine. Question 1: I confirm that I have deployed the virtual machine and opened the website.
